hotspot-manager (1.1.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Major upgrade with virtual interface support
  - Virtual interface creation for true concurrent mode
  - hostapd/dnsmasq direct control
  - Ethernet connection sharing support
  - IP forwarding and NAT configuration
  - Multiple fallback methods

